<https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/github-skills-acquire-codebase-knowledge-assets-templates-structure-md/interior> {
    <https://ontologist.ai/ns/oe/module/github-skills-acquire-codebase-knowledge-assets-templates-structure-md> db:content """# Codebase Structure

## Core Sections (Required)

### 1) Top-Level Map

List only meaningful top-level directories and files.

| Path | Purpose | Evidence |
|------|---------|----------|
| [path/] | [purpose] | [source] |

### 2) Entry Points

- Main runtime entry: [FILE]
- Secondary entry points (worker/cli/jobs): [FILES or NONE]
- How entry is selected (script/config): [NOTE]

### 3) Module Boundaries

| Boundary | What belongs here | What must not be here |
|----------|-------------------|--""" ;
        db:created "2024-04-20" ;
        db:id "STRUCTURE" ;
