| File | Ecosystem | Key fields to read |
|------|-----------|--------------------|
| `package.json` | Node.js / JavaScript / TypeScript | `dependencies`, `devDependencies`, `scripts`, `main`, `type`, `engines` |
| `go.mod` | Go | Module path, Go version, `require` block |
| `""" a rdfs:Resource,
