[run unit tests]
[run integration/e2e tests]
[run coverage]
```

### 2) Test Layout

- Test file placement pattern: [co-located/tests folder/etc]
- Naming convention: [pattern]
- Setup files and where they run: [paths]

### 3) Test Scope Matrix

| Scope | Covered? | Typical target | Notes |
|-------|---""" ;
