# Testing Patterns

## Core Sections (Required)

### 1) Test Stack and Commands

- Primary test framework: [NAME + VERSION]
- Assertion/mocking tools: [TOOLS]
- Commands:

```bash
[run all tests]
[run unit tests]
[run integration/e2e tests]
[run coverage]
```

### 2) Test Layout

- Test file placement pattern: [co-located/tests folder/etc]
- Naming convention: [p""" ;
